comment._content:
Harold Harry Abell [his birth and baptism are shown with both Christian names] was born in 1893 in Leicester. He and his family emigrated to Brisbane, Australia on 28 January 1909. The passenger manifest for the Oswestry Grange shows: 
George Abell, Bootmaker, 43 / Mary, 42 / Millicent, 7 / George, 20 /  Frank, 19 /  Harold, 15 / Nellie, 13.

The ship arrived in Brisbane on 25 Mar 1909.
